---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { getFeaturedProjects, getStackColorClasses } from "../data/projects";

const featuredProjects = getFeaturedProjects();
---

<Layout>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="flex flex-col gap-6 sm:gap-8 px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-20 py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-[120px] w-full">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:gap-6 w-full">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
        <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#22C55E] status-pulse"></div>
        <span class="text-[#22C55E] text-[13px]">// available_for_hire</span>
      </div>
      <span class="text-[#525252] text-sm">$ whoami</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[56px] font-semibold leading-[1.1] max-w-[900px]">
        Full-Stack Engineer<br />Building Digital Experiences
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[#737373] text-base sm:text-lg leading-[1.6] max-w-[800px]">
        I architect scalable systems and craft intuitive interfaces.
        <span class="hidden sm:inline"><br /></span>
        <span class="inline sm:hidden"> </span>
        Specializing in modern technologies including AI, cloud infrastructure, and user interfaces.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch sm:items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4">
      <a href="#projects" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#22C55E] text-[#0C0C0C] text-sm font-medium px-7 py-3.5 rounded btn-glow">
        $ view_projects()
      </a>
      <a href="#" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-[#1A1A1A] text-[#E5E5E5] text-sm font-medium px-7 py-3.5 rounded">
        $ download_resume()
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 sm:gap-6">
      <span class="text-[#525252] text-xs">// tech_stack:</span>
      <span class="text-[#737373] text-xs">TypeScript</span>
      <span class="text-[#737373] text-xs">Go</span>
      <span class="text-[#737373] text-xs">React</span>
      <span class="text-[#737373] text-xs">Next.js</span>
      <span class="text-[#737373] text-xs">PostgreSQL</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Value Section -->
  <section id="about" class="flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-12 px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-20 py-12 lg:py-20 bg-[#0C0C0C] w-full">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 w-full">
      <span class="text-[#525252] text-sm">$ cat ./what_i_bring.md</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold">Engineering Excellence</h2>
      <span class="text-[#525252] text-sm">// the_value_i_deliver</span>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-4 md:gap-6 w-full">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 bg-[#1A1A1A] p-5 md:p-6 rounded flex-1 fade-in-scroll">
        <span class="text-[#22C55E] text-2xl">&gt; </span>
        <h3 class="text-[#E5E5E5] text-base md:text-lg font-medium">code_clarity</h3>
        <p class="text-[#737373] text-[13px] leading-[1.6]">
          Complex problems deserve simple solutions. I write code that's easy to read and maintain—no unnecessary abstractions, no clever tricks. Just clear, pragmatic code that works.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 bg-[#1A1A1A] p-5 md:p-6 rounded flex-1 fade-in-scroll">
        <span class="text-[#3B82F6] text-2xl">&gt; </span>
        <h3 class="text-[#E5E5E5] text-base md:text-lg font-medium">frontend_craft</h3>
        <p class="text-[#737373] text-[13px] leading-[1.6]">
          Building intuitive interfaces with React, Next.js, and Tailwind. I care about the details—the interactions, the performance, the feel. Good UI isn't just functional, it feels right.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 bg-[#1A1A1A] p-5 md:p-6 rounded flex-1 fade-in-scroll">
        <span class="text-[#F59E0B] text-2xl">&gt; </span>
        <h3 class="text-[#E5E5E5] text-base md:text-lg font-medium">systems_at_scale</h3>
        <p class="text-[#737373] text-[13px] leading-[1.6]">
          Go, Postgres, and Kubernetes when the job calls for it. I've built systems serving millions of records to thousands of users daily. Ship it, then optimize where it matters.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Tech Stack Section -->
  <section class="flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-12 px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-20 py-12 lg:py-20 bg-[#1A1A1A] w-full">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 w-full">
      <span class="text-[#525252] text-sm">$ ls ./skills/</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold">Tech Stack</h2>
      <span class="text-[#525252] text-sm">// tools_i_work_with</span>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 w-full">
      <!-- Front-end -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 fade-in-scroll">
        <span class="text-[#22C55E] text-sm font-medium">front_end/</span>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">React</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Next.js</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">TypeScript</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">JavaScript</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">React-Query</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Playwright</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Vitest</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">HTML</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">CSS</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Astro</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Sanity</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Sentry</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Back-end -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 fade-in-scroll">
        <span class="text-[#3B82F6] text-sm font-medium">back_end/</span>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Go</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">NestJS</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Express.js</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">PostgreSQL</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Socket.io</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">MongoDB</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Stripe SDK</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">AWS</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Docker</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Redis</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Ruby on Rails</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Infrastructure -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 fade-in-scroll">
        <span class="text-[#F59E0B] text-sm font-medium">infrastructure/</span>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">GitHub Actions</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Digital Ocean</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Netlify</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Vercel</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">GCP</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">Traefik</span>
          <span class="bg-[#0C0C0C] text-[#A3A3A3] text-xs px-3 py-1.5 rounded">K3s</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Projects Section -->
  <section id="projects" class="flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-12 px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-20 py-12 lg:py-20 bg-[#0C0C0C] w-full">
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-end justify-between gap-4 w-full">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
        <span class="text-[#525252] text-sm">$ ls -la ./projects/</span>
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold">Featured Projects</h2>
        <span class="text-[#525252] text-sm">// selected_work</span>
      </div>
      <a href="/projects" class="text-[#3B82F6] text-[13px] font-medium hover:underline">view_all() &rarr;</a>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 md:gap-6 w-full">
      {featuredProjects.map((project) => (
        <article class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-4 lg:gap-8 bg-[#0C0C0C] p-4 md:p-6 rounded fade-in-scroll">
          <div class="w-full lg:w-[400px] h-[200px] sm:h-[240px] bg-[#1A1A1A] rounded overflow-hidden flex-shrink-0">
            <img src={project.image} alt={project.title} class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 md:gap-4 flex-1">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {project.stack.map((tech) => (
                <span class={`text-[11px] font-medium px-2.5 py-1 rounded ${getStackColorClasses(tech.color)}`}>
                  {tech.name}
                </span>
              ))}
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold">{project.title}</h3>
            <p class="text-[#737373] text-sm leading-[1.6]">
              {project.description}
            </p>
            <a href={project.url} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#22C55E] text-[13px] font-medium hover:underline">&rarr; view_project()</a>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Experience Section -->
  <section id="experience" class="flex flex-col gap-8 md:gap-12 px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-20 py-12 lg:py-20 bg-[#0C0C0C] w-full">
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 w-full">
      <span class="text-[#525252] text-sm">$ git log --oneline ./career/</span>
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold">Work Experience</h2>
      <span class="text-[#525252] text-sm">// commit_history</span>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col w-full">
      <!-- Experience 1 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 md:gap-8 py-6 md:py-8 fade-in-scroll">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 w-full md:w-[180px] lg:w-[200px] flex-shrink-0">
          <span class="text-[#22C55E] text-[13px] font-medium">July 2025 — present</span>
          <span class="text-[#525252] text-[11px]">// 6+ months</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold">Software Engineer @ JobWatchCanada</h3>
          <p class="text-[#737373] text-[13px] leading-[1.6]">
            Built a web app that gathered and visualized hundreds of thousands of Open Government records, amassing 20,000+ unique visitors in its first two months. Featured in Toronto Sun, Toronto Star, Yahoo News, and Canadian Press. Integrated xAi (Grok) for natural language queries on government data.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#525252] text-[11px]">stack:</span>
            <span class="text-[#737373] text-[11px]">Golang, React, MapLibre, xAi/Grok, Pelias</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="h-px bg-[#1F1F1F] w-full"></div>

      <!-- Experience 2 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 md:gap-8 py-6 md:py-8 fade-in-scroll">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 w-full md:w-[180px] lg:w-[200px] flex-shrink-0">
          <span class="text-[#22C55E] text-[13px] font-medium">Mar 2024 — present</span>
          <span class="text-[#525252] text-[11px]">// 1+ year</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold">Customer Success Engineer / Software Engineer @ This Dot</h3>
          <p class="text-[#737373] text-[13px] leading-[1.6]">
            Conducted user research calls to improve onboarding and foster customer retention. Reduced customer support tickets by 25% through server log analysis and troubleshooting. Created comprehensive documentation that reduced support tickets by an additional 50%.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#525252] text-[11px]">stack:</span>
            <span class="text-[#737373] text-[11px]">React, TypeScript, NestJS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="h-px bg-[#1F1F1F] w-full"></div>

      <!-- Experience 3 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-2 md:gap-8 py-6 md:py-8 fade-in-scroll">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-1 w-full md:w-[180px] lg:w-[200px] flex-shrink-0">
          <span class="text-[#737373] text-[13px] font-medium">Sept 2021 — Sept 2023</span>
          <span class="text-[#525252] text-[11px]">// 2 years</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3 flex-1">
          <h3 class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold">Software Engineer @ This Dot</h3>
          <p class="text-[#737373] text-[13px] leading-[1.6]">
            Built a Google Drive app for Stripe that amassed 30,000+ installs. Partnered with Stripe's development team to validate the Stripe Apps platform pre-release. Subject Matter Expert on 2 green-field applications on the Stripe Apps platform.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="text-[#525252] text-[11px]">stack:</span>
            <span class="text-[#737373] text-[11px]">React, TypeScript, NestJS</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section id="contact" class="flex flex-col items-center gap-6 sm:gap-8 px-4 sm:px-8 md:px-12 lg:px-20 py-16 lg:py-[100px] bg-[#1A1A1A] w-full">
    <span class="text-[#525252] text-sm">$ ./connect.sh</span>
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-center leading-[1.2] max-w-[800px]">
      Let's Build Something<br />Together
    </h2>
    <span class="text-[#737373] text-sm sm:text-base text-center">// open_to_opportunities && interesting_projects</span>

    <a href="mailto:hi@tyrelchambers.com" class="flex items-center bg-[#22C55E] text-[#0C0C0C] text-sm font-medium px-8 py-4 rounded btn-glow">
      $ send_email()
    </a>

    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-6">
      <span class="text-[#525252] text-xs">// find_me_on:</span>
      <a href="https://github.com/tyrelchambers?tab=repositories" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#737373] text-[13px] hover:text-[#22C55E] transition-colors">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/tyrel-chambers-8ab581214/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#737373] text-[13px] hover:text-[#22C55E] transition-colors">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://x.com/imtyrelchambers" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-[#737373] text-[13px] hover:text-[#22C55E] transition-colors">Twitter</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
